ActCanada Post Corporation Act
SubjectRegulations Amending The Mail Receptacles Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the MAIL RECEPTACLES REGULATIONS in order to (1) update the dimensional specifications for mail and parcel boxes used in apartment buildings and office complexes; and (2) permit the installation of parcel boxes either inside or outside apartment buildings and office complexes.
